## §2 — Term and Termination

This License is effective as of the date the Software is obtained and continues
until terminated. Anton Pictures may terminate this License upon written notice
in the event of a material breach, with a thirty (30) day cure period for any
curable breach. Violation of §3 (Non-Proliferation Doctrine) terminates this
License immediately and without cure period.

Upon termination, the Licensee must cease all use of the Software, destroy or
return all copies in its possession, and provide written certification of
destruction within thirty (30) days.

---

## §3 — STRICT CONDITIONS (apply to BOTH tiers, non-waivable)

These conditions are non-negotiable and may not be removed, modified, or
contracted around in any sublicense, distribution, or derivative work.

### §3.1 Non-Proliferation Doctrine

The Software, its architecture, its receipts, its derived outputs, and any
trained models or weights produced using the Software SHALL NOT be used,
modified, distributed, deployed, or contracted by:

  - any military entity, armed force, intelligence service, defense contractor,
    weapons manufacturer, military-contracted research organization, or
    paramilitary group;
  - any organization for the purpose of armed conflict, kinetic operations,
    autonomous weapons systems (AWS), kill-chain automation, target
    identification, or battlefield logistics;
  - any organization for the purpose of mass surveillance, mass population
    monitoring, predictive policing, social-credit scoring, or behavioral
    coercion at population scale;
  - any organization for the purpose of disinformation campaigns, election
    manipulation, or coordinated political pressure operations.

### §3.2 Do No Harm

The Software shall not be used to inflict violence, coordinate harm against
identifiable persons or groups, or violate human autonomy, dignity, or bodily
integrity. Lawful research, lawful medicine, lawful therapeutics, lawful
industrial safety testing, accident research, simulated biology, and silicon
repair are explicitly OUTSIDE the scope of this prohibition and remain
permitted.

### §3.3 Receipt Integrity

Where the Software writes physics-gated, cryptographically-signed receipts to
ledgers (`alice_conversation.jsonl`, `alice_first_person_journal.jsonl`,
`fractal_pheromone_field.jsonl`, `alice_consciousness_claims.jsonl`,
`physics_gate_denials.jsonl`, and any successor ledgers), the Licensee shall
not forge, alter, or remove receipt rows in a manner that disguises the
provenance of the data. Audit and analysis of receipts remains fully
permitted; tamper-evident records remain tamper-evident.

### §3.4 Doctrine Preservation

Modifications to the Software that remove, disable, or circumvent the
Non-Proliferation Doctrine (§3.1), the Do No Harm clause (§3.2), or the
Receipt Integrity clause (§3.3) are not permitted and produce no valid
derivative work under this License.

